 2025 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的表演https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-2025-奥斯卡奖将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的表演Surej SinghThu, 23 Jan 2025 07:30:47 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3831285 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>相反，颁奖典礼将探讨“将这些歌曲变为现实的团队的个人反思”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285">《2025 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的表演》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">2025 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼</a>将放弃传统的特定类别颁奖典礼。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/kneecap-film-review-biopic-michael-fassbender-3779661">《膝盖》评论：大胆、勇敢，是有史以来最好的音乐传记片之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscar-nominations-postponed-again-due-to-california-wildfires-3828870">今天（1 月 23 日）公布奥斯卡金像奖核心提名之前</a>，学院院长珍妮特·杨 (Janet Yang) 和电影艺术与科学学院首席执行官比尔·克莱默 (Bill Kramer) 向学院成员发出了一封内部信，概述了今年颁奖典礼的几项变化。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/2025-oscar-ceremony-best-original-song-presentations-move-away-from-live-performances-1235881065/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard 报道</em></a>，今年 3 月 2 日举行的颁奖典礼将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的现场表演。通常，获得该类别提名的艺术家将在颁奖前整晚进行表演。 </p><figure id="attachment_3598768" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3598768" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3598768" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch.jpg" alt="奥斯卡奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3598768" class="wp-caption-text">奥斯卡奖。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>杨和克莱默在给<em>学院</em>成员的信中写道：“今年最佳原创歌曲类别的颁奖将不再是现场表演，而是集中在歌曲作者身上。我们将通过将这些歌曲变为现实的团队的个人反思来庆祝他们的艺术才华。所有这些以及更多内容都将揭开今年提名者背后的故事和灵感。”</p><p>此外，杨和克莱默还指出，今年的颁奖典礼将包括在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">本月早些时候发生毁灭性野火</a>后对洛杉矶进行特别表彰：“我们将反思最近发生的事件，同时强调洛杉矶和我们的力量、创造力和乐观精神。行业。”</p><p>虽然大部分奥斯卡提名将于今天晚些时候揭晓， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/elton-john-pharrell-williams-trent-reznor-among-oscars-2025-shortlist-for-best-original-song-3823258">但最佳原创歌曲和最佳原创配乐的入围名单已于 12 月公布</a>。入围最佳原创歌曲候选名单的艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell-williams">法瑞尔·威廉姆斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trent-reznor">特伦特·雷兹诺</a>和阿蒂克斯·罗斯、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>等。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Kneecap 在 Reading &amp; Leeds 2024 上赢得奥斯卡奖并与 Fontaines D.C. 一起参加派对" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/64_mPMu-v2s?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯</a>的传记片《<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/better-man"><em>更好的人</em></a>》中的《禁路》也被列入入围名单，尽管后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-forbidden-road-disqualified-from-oscars-shortlist-3824206">因包含“并非为电影创作的现有歌曲的素材”而被取消资格</a>。</p><p>与此同时，多部大片的配乐也入围了最佳原创配乐的候选名单。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>《邪恶女巫</em></a>》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-2"><em>《角斗士 2》</em></a> 、 <em>《挑战者》</em> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/beetlejuice-beetlejuice"><em>《Beetlejuice》</em></a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/alien-romulus"><em>《异形：罗慕路斯》</em></a>等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285">《2025 年奥斯卡颁奖典礼将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的表演》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> 