son@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/eminem-janet-jackson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/eminem-janet-jackson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2025年歌曲作者名人堂的入选者名单已揭晓 - 不包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">Eminem</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janet-jackson">Janet Jackson</a>等提名的行为。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/eminem-the-death-of-slim-shady-coup-de-grace-album-review-3774875">Eminem  - “ Slim Shady的死亡（Coup deGrâce）”评论：精心制作的歌曲和空洞的挑衅</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（1月22日），词曲作者名人堂<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-janet-jackson-and-boy-george-among-2025-songwriters-hall-of-fame-nominees-3812190">在11月宣布提名人</a>之后<a href="https://www.songhall.org/news/view/songwriters_hall_of_fame_announces_2025_inductees">，宣布了2025年级的入选者</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-clinton">乔治·克林顿（George Clinton）</a> ，杜比兄弟（Doobie Brothers），阿什利·戈利（Ashley Gorley），罗德尼·杰金斯（Rodney Jerkins），迈克·洛夫（Mike Love）和托尼·麦考雷（Tony Macaulay）入选词曲作者名人堂。</p><p>在11月提名但未裁员的艺术家中，有Eminem，Janet Jackson， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boy-george">Boy George</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alanis-morissette">Alanis Morissette</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sheryl-crow">Sheryl Crow</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nwa">NWA</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bryan-adams">Bryan Adams</a>等。共有26位艺术家获得了提名，只有6名被选为入选。</p><p>六名入选者将于6月在纽约市的2025年入选和颁奖晚会上获得荣誉。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812191" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812191" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812191" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/eminem-janet-jackson-boy-george@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/eminem-janet-jackson-boy-george@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/eminem-janet-jackson-boy-george@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/eminem-janet-jackson-boy-george@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/eminem-janet-jackson-boy-george@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/eminem-janet-jackson-boy-george@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/eminem-janet-jackson-boy-george@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812191" class="wp-caption-text"> Eminem，Janet Jackson和Boy George。学分：Scott Legato/Getty Images，Gilbert Flores/WWD通过Getty Images和Karwai Tang/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rem-steely-dan-timbaland-more-inducted-songwriters-hall-of-fame-2024-3572622">2024年的入选者</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/r-e-m">REM</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timbaland">Timbaland</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steely-dan">Steely Dan</a> ，Hillary Lindsey和Dean Pitchford，辛迪·沃克（Cindy Walker）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">王子（Prince）</a>接受了死后的入选。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">Sza</a>和Diane Warren也获得了特别奖项。</p><p> 2023年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jade">Jade</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/electric-light-orchestra">Electric Light Orchestra的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-lynne">Jeff Lynne</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gloria-estefan">Gloria Estefan</a> ，Teddy Riley，Glen Ballard和Liz Rose一起领导了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-and-sade-among-acts-to-be-inducted-into-songwriters-hall-of-fame-3383545">那年的歌曲作者名人堂入选者</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对Eminem最新专辑“ The Death of Slim Shady（Coup deGrâce）”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/eminem-the-death-of-slim-shady-coup-de-grace-album-review-3774875">三星级评论</a>中写道：“更强大的是&#39;临时&#39;，这是对他的女儿Hailie的真正感动的颂歌，这证明了Marshall Mathers可以可以说出他想何时重要的事情。</p><p> “那么，谁杀死了Slim Shady？在将他带回到光明并表现出无关紧要的时，也许阿姆（Eminem）永久地完成了他的老朋友。好的，我们明白了 - 阴暗是一个令人震惊的角色。现在他已经死了，如何获得一些新材料？”</p><p>在其他与阿姆相关的新闻中，这位说唱歌手 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">在即将到来的格莱美奖中获得最佳说唱表演的提名</a>- 他分享说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-says-kendrick-lamar-is-gonna-sweep-that-shit-at-2025-grammys-3825935">他认为肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）可能会获得他提名的所有七个奖项</a>，肯德里克（Kendrick 。他要去，他应该。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-janet-jackson-and-more-snubbed-for-songwriters-hall-of-fame-3831253">Eminem，Janet Jackson和更多的歌曲作者名人堂的更冷落</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
